"tab. This opens the :guilabel:`Create Sales Team Members` pop-up window. "
"Assign a salesperson in the :guilabel:`Salesperson` field and adjust their "
"lead assignment rules if desired under the :guilabel:`Lead Assignment` tab. "
"Click the :guilabel:`Save & Close` button to finish, or "
"click :guilabel:`Save & New` to open a blank form and keep adding sales team "
