#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/rental_orders/create_rental_order.rst:52
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-clock-o` :guilabel:`Recorded`: Linked to the **Timesheets** app "
"and shows how many hours are related to the rental order."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/rental_orders/create_rental_order.rst:54
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-tasks` :guilabel:`Planned`: Linked to the **Planning** app and "
"shows how many shifts are related to the rental order."
