#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:3
msgid "Invoice project milestones"
msgstr "فوترة معالم المشروع"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:8
msgid ""
"Milestone-based invoicing is designed for companies that deliver work in "
"clearly defined phases. Instead of invoicing an entire service upfront or at "
"the very end, businesses can bill customers progressively as each stage of "
"work is completed. This approach provides customers clearer visibility into "
"progress and value delivered over time."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Odoo, milestone invoicing is configured at the product level in the "
"**Sales** app, with milestone progress and completion managed in the "
"**Projects** app. When a milestone is marked as reached, the delivered "
"quantity on the sales order (SO) is updated and can be invoiced."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:18
msgid "How milestone invoicing works"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:20
msgid ""
"Milestone invoicing follows a clear workflow involving multiple applications "
"in Odoo:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:22
msgid ""
"A product is created in the **Sales** application, configured to be invoiced "
"based on milestones."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:23
msgid "A |SO| is created with the product."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:24
msgid ""
"A project in the **Projects** app is created with multiple milestones "
"included."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:25
msgid ""
"A milestone is reached, and marked complete, causing the *Delivered* "
"quantity on the |SO| line to update."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:27
msgid ""
"An invoice is created for the completed milestone, which can be sent to the "
"customer."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:30
msgid ""
"This document covers the **Sales** app configuration and invoicing flow for "
"invoicing based on project milestones. For more information on creating, "
"managing, and marking milestones as complete, and how to link them to tasks, "
"see :doc:`Project milestones <../../../services/project/project_management/"
"project_milestones>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:36
msgid "Create milestone products"
msgstr "إنشاء منتجات المعالم"

