"the :icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`(area chart)` icon or :icon:`oi-view-"
"pivot` :guilabel:`(pivot)` icon, click :guilabel:`Measures` drop-down button "
"and change it to :guilabel:`Margin` to see margin contributions across the "
"customer base."
